videos.description: James Harden lobs it up to Tarik Black who finishes the alley-oop with a mean one-handed jam.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One Play (Black rises for alley-oop slam) 2018/03/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Black rises for alley-oop slam

videos.description: Alan Williams gets open inside the paint to receive the pass from Shaquille Harrison then scores a basket for a chance at a 3-point play.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Williams scores easy and-1 layup) 2018/03/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Williams scores easy and-1 layup

videos.description: With less than six minutes left in the game, Clint Capela finds PJ Tucker on the outside and he scores from deep to make it a 1-point game against the Suns.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tucker hits big 3 to trim deficit) 2018/03/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tucker hits big 3 to trim deficit

videos.description: James Harden splashes in a triple from the top of the key to tie the game at 101-101.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Harden pulls up for 3 to tie game) 2018/03/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Harden pulls up for 3 to tie game

videos.description: With less than two seconds left, Gerald Green drills a 3-pointer from the corner as the clock expires to give the Rockets a 104-103 win against the Suns.
videos.headline: Green nails epic game-winning 3
